accessibility.text: Arrived Friday, April 3 from Shenzhen, China
Build took 3 hours using included Creality instructions and Youtube set-up videos.
May have over tightened eccentric bolts which caused Z Axis binding and wheel issue.
Purchased a fire blanket, smoke detectors and fire extinguisher.
